OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778922392
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 65-year-old woman
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man from Durrington was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,8,Fassaulting a police officer. He
OL,9,Fremains in custody.
OL,11,FPolice say the victim and suspect knew
OL,12,Feach other.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Amanda Zinyama,
OL,15,Ffrom the Major Crime Team, said: "This
OL,16,Fis a tragic incident, and our thoughts
OL,17,Fare with the woman's loved ones at
OL,18,Fthis difficult time.
OL,26,@wD@bOU
