PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778922392
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 65-year-old woman
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,F"We are in the early stages of a fast-
OL,7,Fmoving investigation, and officers are
OL,8,Fcarrying out extensive enquiries to
OL,9,Festablish the full circumstances.
OL,11,F"While we understand this incident
OL,12,Fwill cause concern locally, we believe
OL,13,Fit to be isolated, with no threat to
OL,14,Fthe wider community, and we are not
OL,15,Fcurrently looking for anyone else in
OL,16,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,18,F"There will be an increased police
OL,19,Fpresence in the area while enquiries
OL,20,Fare ongoing."
